<h1>BookController Documentation</h1>
<p>The BookController provides APIs for managing books in the bookstore.</p>

<h2>API Endpoints</h2>
<table>
    <tr>
        <th>Endpoint</th>
        <th>HTTP Method</th>
        <th>Description</th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>/api/Book/{id}</td>
        <td>GET</td>
        <td>Retrieves a book by its ID.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>/api/Book/Details/{id}</td>
        <td>GET</td>
        <td>Retrieves the detailed information of a book by its ID.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>/api/Book/GetAll</td>
        <td>GET</td>
        <td>Retrieves all books.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>/api/Book/UpdateDetails/{id}</td>
        <td>PUT</td>
        <td>Updates the details of a book.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>/api/Book/Update{id}</td>
        <td>PUT</td>
        <td>Updates a book.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>/api/Book/Create</td>
        <td>POST</td>
        <td>Creates a new book with authors.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>/api/Book/{id}</td>
        <td>DELETE</td>
        <td>Deletes a book by its ID.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>/api/Book/Search/{bookName}</td>
        <td>GET</td>
        <td>Searches for books by name.</td>
    </tr>
</table>

<h2>Response Status Codes</h2>
<ul>
    <li>200 - OK: The request was successful.</li>
    <li>400 - Bad Request: The request was malformed or invalid.</li>
    <li>404 - Not Found: The requested resource was not found.</li>
    <li>500 - Internal Server Error: An unexpected error occurred on the server.</li>
</ul>

